        <a name="whatsNew"></a>
        <h3>What's new</h3>
        <p>The latest release includes the following enhancements:</p>
        <ul>
			<li>Mapping
				<ul>
					<li>You can now <a href="/en/bao/help/color-coded-maps.htm#ESRI_SECTION1_9D4AC04967C74935AC554C1D3881E4AA">browse and select the 2015 Dominant Tapestry Segment</a> when creating a color-coded map in the U.S. </li>
					<li>Access to Web Maps is now available from the "Create Maps from Data" menu. </li>
					<li>New options in Preferences are available to change color and thickness of boundary borders.</li>
					<li>The ability to display boundary borders and labels is now available for all countries.</li>
				</ul></li>
			<li>Display enhancements for sites, businesses, and imported points
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/en/bao/help/set-preferences.htm#ESRI_SECTION1_59C5E4CD30894567AC66F46A03A2D49B">Import and store logos to represent locations that you import</a> or business locations from Business and Facilities Search.</li>
					<li>Set the default symbol for sites, imported files, and business and facilities search results.</li>
					<li>New options for displaying point data are now available with a new mapping option in <a href="/en/bao/help/import-file.htm">Import File</a> and in <a href="/en/bao/help/business-and-faciilties-search.htm">Business and Facilities Search</a>.</li>
					<li>Reorder saved variables.</li>
				</ul></li>
			<li>New ways to create trade areas
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/en/bao/help/find-location.htm#ESRI_SECTION1_F2E39735F3D44A7F9262BDB3260AF922">Create trade areas around sites based on walk time or distance</a>.  Walk times follow paths and roads that allow pedestrian traffic and find solutions that optimize travel time/distance.</li>
					<li>Reports using bands can be applied to rings, drive times, and walk times.</li>
					<li><a href="/en/bao/help/find-location.htm#ESRI_SECTION1_58E891D8C6334263B6F8E6444A39AEE4">More options are available for drive time analysis</a> including travel mode (driving, rural driving, and trucking), direction to or from a facility, and traffic. Traffic options include live traffic or traffic based on typical conditions.</li>
				</ul></li>
			<li>Content Updates
				<ul>
					<li>Infogroup is the <a href="/en/esri-demographics/data/business.htm">new Business Locations/Business Search provider</a> in the U.S. and Canada.</li>
					<li><a href="/en/esri-demographics/data/retail-marketplace.htm">Retail MarketPlace Profile and data</a> have been updated to include business summary counts from Infogroup.</li>
					<li><a href="/en/esri-demographics/data/shopping-centers.htm">Major Shopping Center Locator and Major Shopping Center Map</a> have been updated to include June 2015 data from Directory of Major Malls (DMM).</li>
					<li>Advanced Demographic Datasets are now available. <ul><li>Choose either the Standard data, from Michael Bauer Research (MBR), or the Advanced data.</li></ul></li>
					<li><a href="/en/esri-demographics/data/north-america.htm">Canada 2015 demographic updates</a> (from Environics Analytics).</li>
					<li><a href="http://blogs.esri.com/esri/arcgis/2015/11/04/upcoming-november-2015-release-demographic/">Updates to 45 countries</a> (Standard MBR Data Update).</li>
				</ul></li>
		</ul>
		
